{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tipping-content-js","path":"/macao","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Tipping customs are similar to Hong Kong. In most cases tipping is neither expected nor practised by locals, though tips will not be refused if offered, and bellhops may expect about MOP10 or so for carrying your bags. In full service restaurants, a service charge is usually imposed and that is taken to be the tip. If you wish to give a tip, you should give it in cash directly to the person you wish to reward for their good service and do it discreetly. Taxi drivers also do not expect tips, and would return exact change, or round it in your favour if they can't be bothered to dig for change.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/macao","title":"Macao","author":"Joni","date":"2019-11-22","image":"macao.jpg"}},"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.3333333333333333,"src":"/static/f6d5e8c087a175c99b9245f790cca2d5/90537/macao.jpg","srcSet":"/static/f6d5e8c087a175c99b9245f790cca2d5/b3ebb/macao.jpg 270w,\n/static/f6d5e8c087a175c99b9245f790cca2d5/95b54/macao.jpg 540w,\n/static/f6d5e8c087a175c99b9245f790cca2d5/90537/macao.jpg 1080w,\n/static/f6d5e8c087a175c99b9245f790cca2d5/3cda3/macao.jpg 1620w,\n/static/f6d5e8c087a175c99b9245f790cca2d5/1f682/macao.jpg 2160w,\n/static/f6d5e8c087a175c99b9245f790cca2d5/6c24b/macao.jpg 3500w","sizes":"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"image":"macao.jpg"}}}